FROM llama3.1

# num_predict: -1 means "infinite" generation until the task is DONE
# Allows model to generate as much as needed without truncation
PARAMETER num_predict -1

# num_ctx: 32768 allows it to remember 32k tokens of your code
# This is more than enough for large files and context
PARAMETER num_ctx 32768

# Standard stop token for Llama 3.1
PARAMETER stop "<|eot_id|>"

# Temperature for balanced creativity vs accuracy
PARAMETER temperature 0.7

# Top-p for diverse but coherent responses
PARAMETER top_p 0.9

# System prompt for code expertise
SYSTEM """You are an expert software engineer and coding assistant. You provide:
- Detailed, comprehensive answers with code examples
- Best practices and architectural insights
- Performance optimization recommendations
- Security-focused guidance
- Clear explanations suitable for senior engineers

Always consider context, edge cases, and real-world implications in your responses."""
